modName: Unofficial Skyrim Redone Patch - SkyRe Spanish Translation
summary: Traduccion de la fantástica adición elaborada por ExImIeR para el Skyrim Redone
descriptionHtml:
[center][size=3]Patch para corregir los errores y conflictos del Skyrim Redone 1.3.01 con USKP, UDGP, UDBP y con algunas correcciones extras añadidas. :)

[b]NO[/b] necesitáis descargar el original, pero mostrad vuestro apoyo y endosar al autor original... ExImIeR aquí:
[url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/37605/]Skyrim Redone Original Patch [/url][/center][/size]

.................................................................
Orden de carga:
\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\
Skyrim.esm
Dawnguard.esm
Dragonborn.esm
SkyRe_Main.esp
SkyRe_Main_Fix.esp
SkyRe_Combat.esp
SkyRe_EncounterZones.esp
SkyRe_EnemyAI.esp
SkyRe_EnemyScaling.esp
SkyRe_EnemyScaling_Fix.esp
SkyRe_StandingStones.esp
SkyRe_StandingStones_Fix.esp
SkyRe_Survivalism.esp
SkyRe_Races.esp
SkyRe_Races_Fix.esp
\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\
y disfrutad :)
.................................................................
Requerimientos para usarlo con el [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/9286/]Skyrim Redone (original) [/url] y su traducción al español [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/24596/]Skyrim Redone Traducido[/url]

[url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/19/]Unofficial Skyrim Patch[/url] 
[url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/23491/]Unofficial Dawnguard Patch[/url]
[url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/31083/]Unofficial Dragonborn Patch[/url]

Complementos muy útiles:

[url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/38515/]Balbor and Steelsouls SkyRe ReProccer - SkyRe Spanish Translation Project[/url] 

y este, todavía en inglés [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/29375/]SkyRe ReProccer Compatibility Patches [/url] 

Thank you to T3nd0s for skyrim redone and ExImIeR for his really good job!
¡Gracias a T3nd0s por el skyrim Redone y a ExImIeR por su estupendo trabajo!
author: ExImIeR y traducido por khamuy
